INFO.name: QUERY
INFO.value: WITH region AS (SELECT * FROM ivoa_nsc_dr2.siav1 WHERE q3c_radial_query(s_ra,s_dec,227.5251615214173,-27.026013823449265,2.0)) SELECT * FROM region WHERE ((abs(spat_hilimit1 - spat_lolimit1) < 90.0 AND (227.5251615214173 BETWEEN spat_lolimit1 AND spat_hilimit1) AND (-27.026013823449265 BETWEEN spat_lolimit2 AND spat_hilimit2) ) OR (abs(spat_hilimit1 - spat_lolimit1) > 90.0 AND ((227.5251615214173 BETWEEN 0.0 AND spat_lolimit1) OR (227.5251615214173 BETWEEN spat_hilimit1 AND 360.0) ) AND (-27.026013823449265 BETWEEN spat_lolimit2 AND spat_hilimit2) )) limit 10001
